headline: Hess Midstream LP Schedules Earnings Release Conference Call
summary: HOUSTON, October 20, 2025--Hess Midstream LP (NYSE: HESM) ("Hess Midstream") announced today that it will hold a conference call on Monday, November 3, 2025, at 10:00 a.m. Eastern Time to discuss its third quarter 2025 earnings release.

headline: ExxonMobil Expands Reach With Guyanese Crude Exports to India
summary: XOM expands global footprint as it sells 4 million barrels of Guyanese crude to Indian refiners, marking India's first purchase of new Golden Arrowhead grade amid moves to diversify oil sources.
